This paper deals with the design of a scalable, distributed stream processing system for RFID tracking and monitoring. It involves techniques for distributed inference and query processing, which are relevant to the areas of database systems (cs.DB), distributed computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), networked information systems (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY).
